{"tid":364023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 台灣無業男偷百人斬武士刀　 襲擊總統府站崗憲兵","createTime":"2017-08-18T05:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T13:47:10.000Z","uid":35519,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fabe512183a763db33855718d574e5d47f5cf9ae","tid":364023,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pics.ctitv.com/wpimg/2017/08/20170818002857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpics.ctitv.com%2Fwpimg%2F2017%2F08%2F20170818002857.jpg&h=bca556e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n ▲男子闖入軍史館偷竊武士刀，隨後持刀闖入總統府，砍傷憲兵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總統府今上午10時30分舉辦親子日，一名呂姓男子卻帶著預藏的武士刀欲翻牆入府，遭憲兵制止，男子就用武士刀砍傷憲兵。根據警方初步調查，凶器來源是呂男今早持鐵鎚至貴陽街軍史館竊取一把武士刀，赴總統府行凶，呂男供稱是要彰顯政治立場，<strong><ins>且在隨身包包內發現五星旗</ins></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pics.ctitv.com/wpimg/2017/08/20170818002986.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpics.ctitv.com%2Fwpimg%2F2017%2F08%2F20170818002986.jpg&h=6e82da12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n憲兵202指揮部政戰主任張博彥上校受訪表示，這名男子是在10時10分左右闖入西大門，<strong><ins>持武士刀砍傷憲兵右側脖子，傷口約10公分，第一時間送台大醫院急診，已無大礙。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20170818123129440886.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20170818123129440886.jpg&h=315bd1a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今早總統府周姓憲兵突遭遭暴徒以隨身刀械所傷，嫌疑犯目前已送介壽路派出所問訊當中。圖為呂姓嫌犯移送畫面。"},{"pid":"5277e58b1f6a39f722c8250288f0c88042ad2671","tid":364023,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"砍憲兵武士刀曝光！上刻「南京之役殺107人」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20170818/640_d7dfc08256fd6ba8a420101b08ad4ca9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170818%2F640_d7dfc08256fd6ba8a420101b08ad4ca9.jpg&h=f7ee9ee8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子闖入總統府，先在軍史館偷走「南京大屠殺」的日本武士刀，再用來砍殺憲兵，現在這把刀也曝了光。<br />\n<br />\n據網路上有研究有關此刀史實者的介紹，這把武士刀來源，據說是1945年冬天收繳投降日軍武器時，時任國民黨第16軍22師輜重兵營營長的余鴻成，接收日軍第一旅團的10把軍刀之一，而這軍刀為九八式軍刀，刀身在刀刃近護手處的銅制夾刃上，還刻有&ldquo;南京之役殺一○七人&rdquo;的字樣。(即時新聞中心/綜合報導)"},{"pid":"c03becfa84b58b6afec89be698c608ff7cea23b2","tid":364023,"uid":35519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:13:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://disp.cc/b/163-accM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fb%2F163-accM&d=vlsB%2B7gJl9gGXUKSlXAUQKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=becd39d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://disp.cc/b/163-accM</a><br />\n作者 kurtsgm ()<br />\n : 〔記者劉慶侯／台北報導〕警方調查，51歲嫌犯呂軍億，家住北投地區，目前無業，也並: 無前科資料。警方在他隨身包包內發現五星旗。<br />\n<br />\n查了一下這個名字，只能說越看越 ㄎㄎ<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n遼寧號編隊一級戰鬥部署通過臺灣海峽 艦載機連續放飛！<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/vT0Go3m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FvT0Go3m.png&h=a2c3c1c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n给爱妻最后的礼物&hellip;&hellip;刘晓波临终手稿曝光<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oHcqJ31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoHcqJ31.png&h=6d7e95d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n1997年人民解放军进驻香港，史无前例的一次和平大进驻<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/uV01NPB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuV01NPB.png&h=446dc33f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n可是軍億，你怎麼把毛主席的名字都搞錯惹呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lpEpgoN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlpEpgoN.png&h=215296a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0c3b7fd00f34c46d080b911ba9cf0f3b4b7e7e0","tid":364023,"uid":48579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b98fefe7fa9b59e812a63b4e0fb2d0aa648e47c2","tid":364023,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T05:15:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=